Entry.JapaneseText: わたしたちも 一緒に行きます！
きみは……！ また会えたね！
なんだ、この前会った 変なヤツじゃないか
Entry.EnglishText: What? You're that weird thing from before.

Entry.JapaneseText: こんなとこまで 追いかけてきたのか？
Entry.EnglishText: Don't tell me you came ALL the way here stalking me!?

Entry.JapaneseText: あ……えっと……ぼくも まさかこんなとこで 会えると思ってなくて……
Entry.EnglishText: I-I didn't know you were here! We came for something else! Really!

Entry.JapaneseText: 僕たちは、 ルナの力を借りに来たんだ
Entry.EnglishText: We've come here hoping to ask Luna for her power.

Entry.JapaneseText: ルナお姉ちゃんの力を？
Entry.EnglishText: You need Luna's help? Please. Don't be so stupid.

Entry.JapaneseText: 魔界の扉を閉じるために、 どうしてもルナの光の力が 必要なんです
Entry.EnglishText: We need to close the door to Daemonium. It's imperative we obtain Luna's assistance.

Entry.JapaneseText: あーっ！ 思い出したぞ
Entry.EnglishText: Wait a second! I remember you!

Entry.JapaneseText: おまえら１００年くらい前に ルナお姉ちゃんを勝手に 連れ出したヤツらだろ
Entry.EnglishText: 100 years ago you came here and abused of poor Luna's kindness and took her from me!

Entry.JapaneseText: その節は お世話になりました
Entry.EnglishText: At that occasion she assisted us on our journey.

Entry.JapaneseText: 帰った帰った。 今度はルナお姉ちゃんを 渡さないからな
Entry.EnglishText: I won't let you take Luna again!

Entry.JapaneseText: 待って！ 教えて！ ぼくのことを！
Entry.EnglishText: Wait! You promised to tell me more about what I am!

Entry.JapaneseText: 知るかよ、 おまえのことなんて！
Entry.EnglishText: You really don't know what you are? I can't do miracles, you know.

Entry.JapaneseText: でも、あそこから出したら 教えてくれるって……
Entry.EnglishText: But you promised that if we got you out of that prison you would tell me...

Entry.JapaneseText: そーだよーだ。あそこから 出たかっただけだっての。 悪いかよ！
Entry.EnglishText: Oh heck yes! You go me out of there already! Tooo baaad!

Entry.JapaneseText: ねぇ、本当に知らないの？ ぼく、ずっと妖精の仲間を 探してたのに……
Entry.EnglishText: You don't know anything at all...? And here I was...searching for my fairy friends for so long...

Entry.JapaneseText: うるさいなぁ！ 知らないって 言ってんだろ！
Entry.EnglishText: Shut up! I TOLD you I know nothing!

Entry.JapaneseText: あ…… エレメンツポットが……
うっ…… そ、そっちが 悪いんだからな！
せっかく…… 集めたのに…… 精霊と戦って……
Entry.EnglishText: All that trouble...fighting the Summon Spirits...all we gathered is now...gone...

Entry.JapaneseText: ゴメン…… オレがちゃんと持って なかったから……
Entry.EnglishText: Sorry... I wasn't holding it strong enough...

Entry.JapaneseText: 違うよ、<DIO>……！ ぼくがぶつかったかラ……
Entry.EnglishText: It's not your fault! It's my fault. It was me who bumped into it...

Entry.JapaneseText: み、皆さん、 元気出してください
Entry.EnglishText: E-everyone, please get a hold of yourselves.

Entry.JapaneseText: 精霊のことは、精霊に 聞けばなんとかなるよ
Entry.EnglishText: If we are talking about Spirits, it is better to listen what other Summon Spirits have to say.

Entry.JapaneseText: ええ、可能性はあります。 ここで希望を捨てるのは よくないと思いますよ
Entry.EnglishText: There's a chance she knows something. Don't cast aside all hope just yet!

Entry.JapaneseText: そ、そうだよな…… 行こう、<MEL>
